<nav-bar page-name="团课预约" class="topNav"></nav-bar>
<!-- 内容 -->
<view class="group_container" style="margin-top:{{navHeight}}px;margin-bottom:{{isFree?'100rpx':'212rpx'}}">
  <view class="group_pic">
    <view class="join_num">已参加1/30</view>
  </view>
  <view class="coach_img">
    <image src="/static/coach01.png"></image>
  </view>
  <!-- 课程开始时间 -->
  <view class="course_date">
    <view class="left">
      <image src="/static/head.png" style="width:53rpx;height:53rpx;" alt=""></image>
      <text class="coachName">六大胖</text>
      <image src="/static/man.png" style="width:40rpx;height:40rpx;"></image>
    </view>
    <view class="right">
      <view>报名开始：2021/3/18 10:00</view>
      <view>截止日期：2021/3/18 12:00</view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="course_name">课程名：动感单车</view>
  <view class="course_time">时间： 2021/3/18 18:00-19:00</view>
  <view class="course_introduce">
    <view class="introduce">介绍：</view>
    <view class="introduce_detail">
      如果运动的过程是快乐的，那么减肥成功就是必然的，通过互动、有趣、科学的方式快速减脂，突破减脂平台期！适合人群：需要瘦身，减肥遇
    </view>
  </view>
  <!-- 免费的团课 -->
  <view class="order_list" wx:if="{{isFree}}">
    <view class="order" bindtap="handleSeat">预约</view>
  </view>
  <!-- 收费的团课 -->
  <view wx:else class="pay_course">
    <view class="pay_list">
      <view class="pay">
        <view class="pay_title">支付方式</view>
        <view class="WeChatPay">
          <text>微信支付</text>
          <image src="/static/bottom_arrow.png"></image>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="pay_total">
        <view class="pay_number">
          <text>合计：</text>
          <view class="price">20.00元</view>
        </view>
        <view class="pay_order">
          <view class="order_title">预约</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <!-- 选座 -->
  <view class="mask" wx:if="{{chooseSeat}}" bindtap="close">
    <view class="mask-item">
      <view style="padding: 0 30rpx;">
        <view class="seatTitle">选择座位</view>
         <ul class="seatAll">
           <block wx:for="{{20}}">
             <li>
               <view class="seat" catchtap="close">{{index+1}}</view>
             </li>
           </block>
         </ul>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>